dc_description_s: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 1522a. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. Some sheets from this set were revised and issued by War Office. Geographical Section. General Staff, published as G.S.G.S. no. 1522, 1522a. Series covers Mesopotamia and eastern Anatolian parts of Ottoman Empire. "Compiled for the Geographical Section, Generals Staff, War Office, by Lieut. Col F.R. Maunsell, C.M.G. [from] In Nordarabien & Sudmesopotamien by Prinz Sixtus von Bourbon & A. Musil, 1912, 'Vom Mittelmeere zum Persischen Golf' by Max Freiherr von Oppenheim, 1893." With glossary. Set complete, see index.
dc_title_s: Eastern Turkey in Asia. Abu Samakh, sheet 49. Series G.S.G.S. no. 1522a
